name: Custom Valentine:: Paris- Place de la Bastille et Colonne de Juiliet
description:
Je t'aime!  Send an old-fashioned token of love to your sweetie with a unique custom valentine, scribed in calligraphy by Betsy Dunlap on the back of a gorgeous vintage Paris postcard.  Valentines will ship out on February 7th, in time for Valentine's Day. 30 word limit. 

PLEASE PROVIDE YOUR EMAIL ADDRESS IN "MESSAGE TO SELLER" DURING PAYPAL CHECKOUT.  I will email a form for all the customization information.  

Order Includes:
-Vintage Paris postcard with custom message scribed on the back by Betsy Dunlap in jet-black sumi ink.  30 word limit. 
-A2 dutch felt envelope in creamery; archival paper; 32 lb.
-Handcut yellow marbled envelope liners with handmade paper from Bangladesh.
-Vintage postage (combinations of stamps will vary).  
-Swath of gold washi paper tape seals the back envelope flap.
